v0.2 to v0.3.1
--------------
* Added LAN support
* The tool now deletes everything it created under /tmp/
* As from not only connect.sh and disconnect.sh containes code.
  init.sh and boot.sh will exist, but will not execute code, for backward
  compatibility. Connect will do init, boot and connect, while disconnect
  will do diconnect and done.

v0.1 to v0.2-rc1
----------------
* Bugfixes
* Added support for proxy
* Added support for server name (for huji, tau and technion)
* Added support for IMAP email servers
* README aligned to 80-lines width
* Default database directory is now: /usr/share/internet_db/

